

     
      My only pets as a kid were fish.  What a great pet for an impressionable youth.  How long does a fish live -- an hour, an hour and a half? "Thanks, Mom. I almost thought of a name for that one."  Every time my fish would die, I would freeze them in hopes of one day finding a cure.  It didn't work, but it's fun at parties. "Need more ice? I'll be right back. Got to crack a tray of guppies."  Arthur 
     
    
